                                <p class="mb-0">Explore our sandbox environment with sample data from a typical glass production facility.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-highlight mb-4">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-calendar-check me-2 text-primary"></i> Live Walkthrough</h4>
